{"tid":2336658,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[硬件撚]討論硬件知識、砌機LIST、解答問題集中帖(258) 睇#1","createTime":"2020-12-22T18:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T18:32:47.000Z","uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52b5c7525005ee7ceb16da7f69b776fb314114bd","tid":2336658,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOaXH4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOaXH4e.jpg&h=cadf6ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">新人求List需知</span></span></strong><br />\n為方便連登眾巴絲可以幫助你，請你合作<br />\n不但可以令連登眾巴絲可以盡快回覆你的問題<br />\n更可以令條List更適合你所需<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">顯卡係蝗語，請講顯示卡或display card </span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9Li1671.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9Li1671.gif&h=e2849c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">Google是個好東西 發問前可以Google下有無答案先 </span></span></strong><br />\n例如你啲藍mon code巴打們都係Google俾你<br />\n<br />\n[極新手恩物] 教你由零開始選擇硬件砌機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1050181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1050181</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 請講低Budget<br />\nNO MONEY NO TALK ，預算上限寬鬆可以買好一點，預算太低可能要將就或繼續儲錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFQCM1P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFQCM1P.gif&h=c0d97530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦主要用途 <br />\n打機 / 剪片 / 執相 / WORKSTATION<br />\n打機既需唔需要直播或錄製遊戲影片?<br />\n<br />\n3. 個人需求<br />\n玩以上遊戲你最低可接受嘅畫質(Ultra/高/中/低)?最低可接受幾fps(60/144/240)?<br />\n如果你預計會玩新遊戲，想幾耐唔駛升級電腦硬件?<br />\n想唔想超頻?散熱需求如何?使唔使靜過Dyson?<br />\n有冇特定嘅牌子信仰?想唔想有華麗嘅RGB光效?<br />\n<br />\n4. 現在或將會使用mon的類型<br />\n<span class=\"red\">解像度</span>有分1080p, 2K(1440p), 4K(2160p)<br />\n<span class=\"green\">更新頻率</span>有分60Hz, 144Hz, 240Hz<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">畫面比例</span>有分 16:9, 21:9, 32:9<br />\n你想要咩解像度(畫質)同更新頻率(流暢度)?<br />\n解像度高，會對打機效能造成影響，但畫質會更好<br />\n更新頻率高，如效能足夠可以造成比低更新頻率更好嘅流暢度<br />\n<br />\n5. 自己都學習一些<br />\n講真，班巴絲好憎伸手黨，所以建議你行多一兩步<br />\n哪怕你直接照抄悠二伏List放上黎問，佢地都會出手幫助 (<a href=\"http://yujihw.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=8cec6f70\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com/</a>)<br />\n只係Ctrl-C和Ctrl-V咁簡單，大家都會開心嘅事點解唔做呢?<br />\n甚至可能你在過程中已經搵到需要的答案都不一定!<br />\n(砌機list 用作參考 自行格價 可留意實體店鋪 以下網址用方便砌list之用)<br />\n飛馬:<a href=\"https://shop.pegasushk.net/customize-pc/?MTE3MTg=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.pegasushk.net%2Fcustomize-pc%2F%3FMTE3MTg%3D&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=7f474f97\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.pegasushk.net/customize-pc/?MTE3MTg=</a><br />\n法奧:<a href=\"https://www.faroll.com/customize\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faroll.com%2Fcustomize&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=72917e0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.faroll.com/customize</a><br />\n終端:<a href=\"https://www.terminalhk.com/pcSystem/customize/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.terminalhk.com%2FpcSystem%2Fcustomize%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=b8381f89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.terminalhk.com/pcSystem/customize/</a><br />\n<br />\n6. <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">請上銅柱(MB and M.2)</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">重覆檢查插好CPU 4/8/16 pin, MB 24pin, 死人針位(power/reboot/led) </span><br />\n（<span class=\"red\">仲有走好線先</span>）<br />\n<br />\n7. <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">召喚硬件傳心師</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f206G0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff206G0k.jpg&h=4da4ff9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇人知你部機咩spec 呀<br />\n你有咩壞野問題唔該貼返<strong><span class=\"red\">full spec</span></strong><br />\nCPU, MB, RAM, DISPLAY CARD, PSU etc.<br />\nCPU-Z / GPU-Z / HWINFO<br />\n火牛要打開機箱自己睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHv8PLX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHv8PLX.png&h=997c0f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">最好請附上機箱內部圖片一張</span><br />\n<br />\n8.邊到買野好？<br />\n<span class=\"red\">關於所有店舖事項請巴打從其他有效方式聯絡 </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">買前好問問 買後問懵撚</span></strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"violet\">去買野之前 除左銀包之外 記得帶埋個腦去 唔好做水魚</span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">比咗錢印咗單就唔好POST上黎問 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HppkYop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHppkYop.jpg&h=a09ec374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃金：中央田 CentralField, 正都 Capital, 匯訊 Comdex<br />\n旺電：<del>珍寶 Jumbo</del>(慶祝國慶),SE computer<br />\n新高登：G2 System<br />\n高登：高登熊貓電腦<br />\n灣電：<span class=\"orange\">未來科技</span> (雖然係黃 但幾黑)<br />\n<br />\n網店：<br />\n法奧 Faroll <br />\n香港終端 hkterminal<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><del>飛馬</del></span> - (藍店,黑店$1399試用版windows,屌米機做公司客服機將手足客戶資料送中,用大量支那產品,)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2052232/page/1 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2052232/page/1 </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海外：<br />\n<del>新蛋 NewEgg</del>(中資)<br />\n美馬 Amazon<br />\n<br />\n9.AMD 拆cpu cooler 前記得整熱部機<br />\nAmd 拔劍有事幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10. 舊版上新一代CPU記得叫鋪頭Up Bios<br />\n如果唔係開唔到機<br />\n<br />\n11. 檢測效能方法 - Afterburner(AB) + Rivatuner Statistics Server(RTSS)<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">AB為GPU OC software <strong>咩牌子</strong>都用得<br />\n配合埋RTSS 就可以實現OSD 功能</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">有咩用? 如果你發現打機果時lag 或者想知部機依家效能有冇問題<br />\n利用AB + RTSS 就可以即時check 到哂CPU GPU usage 同 tempature. <br />\nEG: CPU/GPU過熱降頻 係咪要改善機箱風道?<br />\nCPU 長期100% 代表粒u 唔夠力</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msi.com/page/afterburner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msi.com%2Fpage%2Fafterburner&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=42193ef0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msi.com/page/afterburner</a><br />\n<br />\n12. Uninstall GPU driver: 換任何卡請DDU 一次<br />\nDDU: <a href=\"https://www.guru3d.com/files-details/display-driver-uninstaller-download.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guru3d.com%2Ffiles-details%2Fdisplay-driver-uninstaller-download.html&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=0a1ab782\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.guru3d.com/files-details/display-driver-uninstaller-download.html</a><br />\n<br />\n13. For Advance Information<br />\nMotherboard VRM資料<br />\namd : <a href=\"https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/pga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hardwareluxx.de%2Fcommunity%2Ff12%2Fpga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=17f1441c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/pga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html</a><br />\nintel : <a href=\"https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/lga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hardwareluxx.de%2Fcommunity%2Ff12%2Flga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=6c3eb6a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/lga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html</a><br />\n全部AM4底板spec：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wmsTYK9Z3-jUX5LGRoFnsZYZiW1pfiDZnKCjaXyzd1o/htmlview#gid=2112472504&amp;fvid=325421275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1wmsTYK9Z3-jUX5LGRoFnsZYZiW1pfiDZnKCjaXyzd1o%2Fhtmlview%23gid%3D2112472504%26fvid%3D325421275&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=d8fb47d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wmsTYK9Z3-jUX5LGRoFnsZYZiW1pfiDZnKCjaXyzd1o/htmlview#gid=2112472504&amp;fvid=325421275</a><br />\nSata / NVME SSD 網上資料 (含Controller, DRAM, NAND Chip Brand資料):<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1B27_j9NDPU3cNlj2HKcrfpJKHkOf-Oi1DbuuQva2gT4/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1B27_j9NDPU3cNlj2HKcrfpJKHkOf-Oi1DbuuQva2gT4%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=058c0c09\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1B27_j9NDPU3cNlj2HKcrfpJKHkOf-Oi1DbuuQva2gT4/edit#gid=0</a><br />\nPSU DB:<br />\n <a href=\"http://www.orionpsudb.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orionpsudb.com%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=3d102f25\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orionpsudb.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n14. 硬件建議LIST (PSU / CASE / COOLER / SSD)<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">COOLER MASTER = 伏</span></strong><br />\n巴打推介 好似係 諗唔到可以係度望下有咩好選擇<br />\n有咩更新搵凌風想幫手update 都可以叫我放edit 權限畀你<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1cllIBhfxPE3ZWsHBZfmj23iwymJTBfj464Zcqg00wxM/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1cllIBhfxPE3ZWsHBZfmj23iwymJTBfj464Zcqg00wxM%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=85bfd3df\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1cllIBhfxPE3ZWsHBZfmj23iwymJTBfj464Zcqg00wxM/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ae21fd2683b303a28585783e1ec305a417c902","tid":2336658,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T18:31:16.000Z","msg":"風扇一律推薦 NOCTUA<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wjh92Xo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjh92Xo.jpg&h=f2ea05ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Noctua Roadmap</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHdhm